{"tid":912572,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"摩洛哥遊記🇲🇦  7日6夜","createTime":"2018-11-22T18:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T08:03:40.000Z","uid":137798,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b62df4d66dc88302d5e41c2d9af076e41b6c0f14","tid":912572,"uid":137798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T18:54:16.000Z","msg":"行程如下<br />\nDay 1 Fez<br />\nDay 2 Fez <br />\nDay 3 Chefchaouen<br />\nDay 4 Marrakech<br />\nDay 5 Sahara Tour (2days 1 night)<br />\nDay 6 Sahara <br />\nDay 7 Marrakech hea &mdash; fez leave <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n背景資料:<br />\n本身自己響法國讀書<br />\n機緣巧合之下揾到朋友都想去摩洛哥🇲🇦<br />\n因為自己未去過非洲<br />\n又覺得呢個地方幾靚<br />\n之後就決定走堂去<br />\n但可惜唔夠時間去Casablanca <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n摩洛哥有用資訊:<br />\n香港護照免簽證30日<br />\n插頭同歐洲一樣-兩頭 <br />\nHong Kong dollar 80:100 Morocco Dirham <br />\n將所有野打八折就係香港價錢<br />\n<br />\n記得 記得 唱定euro/usd 先<br />\n再去到當地唱錢<br />\n用港幣會好低rate <br />\n<br />\n物價比香港平少少<br />\n任何地方買嘢都記得要講價<br />\n佢哋大概會開一個三至四倍嘅價錢<br />\n殺佢價就可以<br />\n<br />\n食一餐正宗摩洛哥菜大概係$250 Dirham <br />\n串燒就大概10 Dirham/串<br />\n一個麥當勞餐50 dirham <br />\n<br />\n城市與城市之間穿梭得巴士(ctm bus) / train (oncf)<br />\n市內就係的士<br />\n可以上網book車飛先<br />\n或者自己去到隨心想玩乜就玩乜<br />\n<br />\n語言方面<br />\n除左旅遊區之外 得部分人識講英文<br />\n大部分都只係識講阿拉伯文同法文<br />\n最好就係朝早出發之前叫酒店reception 幫你寫定哂你想去嘅地方嘅Arabic <br />\n<br />\n注意事項<br />\n女仔一定要小心啲<br />\n佢哋好鍾意望住啲亞洲人<br />\n係心懷不軌的眼神<br />\n盡量避免夜晚岀街<br />\n記得小心銀包同電話！<br />\n<br />\n夜晚摩洛哥係無得買酒<br />\n任何地方都會停止賣酒<br />\n想搵杯啤酒飲到都好困難<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUWZcZH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUWZcZH.png&h=20b086ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fa976jL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffa976jL.png&h=d51a076f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jaCp8x8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjaCp8x8.png&h=7a043695&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VyecxZQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVyecxZQ.png&h=28225c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LG3wOyc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLG3wOyc.png&h=5aea6096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比小小相睇住先<br />\n而家先係行程第二日<br />\n所以可能會出得有啲慢<br />\n有咩想知更多就問！"},{"pid":"8df2f7b39ab7719929b5916c7bcf342347d5edf3","tid":912572,"uid":1666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T20:52:58.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n買左機票1月尾去<br />\nBerlin&lt;-&gt;Marrakech <br />\n同你一樣7日6夜<br />\n你join左邊間Sahara tour?同埋幾錢？<br />\n我諗緊3日2夜定2日1夜<br />\n3日2夜tour 會由Marrakech -&gt; Fes<br />\n另外，我仲會去Chefchaouen <br />\n仲想去Rabat,但驚唔夠時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等你update <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0fee9dfa690a3069e3b5aa783cae8a4c46dc13","tid":912572,"uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T20:58:23.000Z","msg":"你係搭巴士定火車穿梭？<br />\n火車好似幾貴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw<span style=\"color: violet;\">打你老母折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"428d5497e5cb2d912c04f88d007be84b7295c0ec","tid":912572,"uid":50500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T23:07:00.000Z","msg":"你依個真係標準行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9251c0f7470b379cca2e133d40b595dcc0ee36c","tid":912572,"uid":9435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T23:59:33.000Z","msg":"Casablanca 都冇野玩 <br />\n唔駛去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n悶到仆街"},{"pid":"da53917ed3eb66023c3e085bb4465ee6926e4449","tid":912572,"uid":137798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:53:56.000Z","msg":"Day 1-2: Fez (菲斯)<br />\n<br />\n為摩洛哥🇲🇦第二大城市<br />\n僅次於Casablanca <br />\n佢就分左做兩邊:舊城(Medina) &amp; 新城<br />\n新城嗰邊集中左比較好的酒店<br />\n唯一嘅交通工具係的士<br />\n記住同佢講meter, 的士費係人頭計<br />\n不過都建議揾間好少少的酒店住 safety!<br />\n<br />\nMedina &mdash; 裡面有9400幾條街<br />\n譽為全世界最容易迷路城市<br />\n唯一的交通工具就係你對腳<br />\n不過真係唔建議左穿右插<br />\n蕩失路你要比返錢Moroccan 作為問路費<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可蘭經學校 &mdash;  Bou Inania Madrasa <br />\n(20 Dirham/person)<br />\n其實裡面乜都無 只係去欣賞下個建築<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qgChOri.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqgChOri.png&h=ff692c60&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fsu4trk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFsu4trk.png&h=1e4aaced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好近blue gate  唔難揾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DSkbSTm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDSkbSTm.png&h=a37de037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n染布房 &mdash; 要坐petit taxi 特登去<br />\n同埋要當地人帶你去 無可能自己揾到條路<br />\n上到去會有人比塊薄荷葉你 同講解(pay tips again)  夏天會好臭 有心理準備<br />\n最靚嘅係駱駝皮 斜咩袋要700-800 Dirham <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zzCd6du.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzzCd6du.png&h=b7f2f223&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JWtEhkb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJWtEhkb.png&h=c1cf5398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地墊舖<br />\n傳統摩洛哥手藝(都代表好貴)<br />\n呢到既地墊係一代傳一代 家傳之寶咁<br />\n一張放門口嘅要成千蚊港紙<br />\n值吾值就見仁見智<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FSjgjyE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFSjgjyE.png&h=652a7152&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oHBRSTH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoHBRSTH.png&h=6e8b7c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後就係上山睇景<br />\n天氣好可以行響blue gate 行上去 <br />\n25分鐘慢慢行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b3NQ8sk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb3NQ8sk.png&h=a0ca9198&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JbcBjy3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJbcBjy3.png&h=956d55c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFes真係一日半就夠<br />\n同太陽落山就好離開Medina <br />\n裡面無乜街燈   夜晚會幾危險<br />\n不過去到邊都好 都要殺價<br />\n下一站: Chefchouen!"},{"pid":"63d145e08d529cbbcacf1d398becef6b950b89fe","tid":912572,"uid":137798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8df2f7b39ab7719929b5916c7bcf342347d5edf3","tid":912572,"uid":1666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T20:52:58.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n買左機票1月尾去<br />\nBerlin&lt;-&gt;Marrakech <br />\n同你一樣7日6夜<br />\n你join左邊間Sahara tour?同埋幾錢？<br />\n我諗緊3日2夜定2日1夜<br />\n3日2夜tour 會由Marrakech -&gt; Fes<br />\n另外，我仲會去Chefchaouen <br />\n仲想去Rabat,但驚唔夠時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等你update <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:59:38.000Z","msg":"我去2日1夜<br />\n唔夠時間去3日2夜<br />\nOnline book咗先會係2倍價錢<br />\n但guaranteed <br />\n我就決定去到先再揾<br />\n但點都會去 Aït Benhaddou <br />\n<br />\nRabat 雖然係capital<br />\n真係無乜人去<br />\n所以都skip左"},{"pid":"c723b7fbdc4e78e1adf59fd4c5fa12e156df213b","tid":912572,"uid":137798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd0fee9dfa690a3069e3b5aa783cae8a4c46dc13","tid":912572,"uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T20:58:23.000Z","msg":"你係搭巴士定火車穿梭？<br />\n火車好似幾貴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw<span style=\"color: violet;\">打你老母折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兩樣都有<br />\n我響Chefchouen 直接落去Marrakech 坐巴士<br />\n大概係200 Dirham <br />\n要坐10個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n火車就響Marrakach 上返Fes <br />\n我Fes 入 Fes走"},{"pid":"ed350cead83b3b1c57e24d5ee857053f6af54f5b","tid":912572,"uid":137798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"428d5497e5cb2d912c04f88d007be84b7295c0ec","tid":912572,"uid":50500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T23:07:00.000Z","msg":"你依個真係標準行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:03:40.000Z","msg":"其實個trip好rush<br />\n係撞啱Ryanair promotion <br />\n之後先決定去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都無乜人講去摩洛哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}